  Title: Dice
  Description: 'These are your best friend, they''ll help you get points so you can
    pay off your debt.


    Clicking on them BEFORE a roll allows you to drag them,
    swap their position in your egg carton, or put them into your cardboard box.
    Clicking on them AFTER a roll allows you to select dice you want to keep should
    you reroll.'
